表格短消息发送明细的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('CellCentent')
and type = 'U')
drop table CellCentent
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: CellCentent */
/*==============================================================*/
create table CellCentent (
ID int identity(1,1),
CellTel varchar(20) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
CellText varchar(2000) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS not null,
IsFlag bit not null,
CreateTime datetime not null constraint DF_CellCentent_CreateTime default CONVERT([char](19),getdate(),(121)),
constraint PK_CELLCENTENT primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
go
